data.description: Welcome to this beautifully updated and expansive home in the highly desirable and upscale Lake Oswego neighborhood, South Shore Estates. This property offers an elegant and comfortable lifestyle, providing the ultimate tranquility and privacy.  As you walk into the bright and spacious entry, you'll immediately feel at home in the light-filled, beautiful main-floor plan, including a living room with fireplace, formal dining room with wet bar, great room with fireplace and stunning built ins.  The well-appointed kitchen features granite slab countertops, an island with high-end appliances including a Wolf 5 burner gas cooktop and double ovens.  Rounding out the main floor is a half bath, utility room and an amazing den with striking custom coffered wood ceilings and a built in bookshelf and desk. Upstairs you'll find a fabulous primary suite with a stunning view, walk-in closet and a large primary bath with double sinks and jet tub.  The other three bedrooms include high ceilings and plenty of windows, carrying that feeling of natural light throughout the house.  To top it off, enjoy the large bonus room with pool table and lots of storage.  Retreat to your private backyard oasis with all-season colors and thoughtful landscaping that you can enjoy every day from your family room and kitchen. The 3 car oversized garage offers plenty of room for storage plus a lofted storage space within. Close to downtown Lake Oswego and the farmers market, library, top notch schools, shops, great restaurants and Tryon Creek park.  If you love hosting parties or prefer relaxing at home, this property has everything you need.  With intentionally designed spaces, a comfortable and relaxing atmosphere, and the utmost livability, this is THE perfect place to call home. Come take a tour today!
